{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-markdown-page-js","path":"/other/faq","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Shiren SFC Wiki | Zoiteki","docsLocation":"https://github.com/zoiteki/shiren-1/tree/main/content"}},"markdownRemark":{"fields":{"id":"eeacffcf-3c1d-58db-90a7-2d21e62d597a","title":"FAQ","slug":"/other/faq"},"parent":{"relativePath":"other/faq.md"},"frontmatter":{"title":"FAQ","metaTitle":"FAQ - Shiren 1 Wiki","metaDescription":"Frequently Asked Questions for Shiren the Wanderer"},"html":"<h2 id=\"What-is-Mystery-Dungeon\" style=\"position:relative;\">What is Mystery Dungeon?<a href=\"#What-is-Mystery-Dungeon\" aria-label=\"What is Mystery Dungeon permalink\" class=\"custom-class after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.65 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h2>\n<p>Mystery Dungeon is a series of roguelike games developed by Chunsoft / Spike Chunsoft. The series\r\nbegan with Torneko's Great Adventure: Mystery Dungeon, featuring Torneko from Dragon Quest 4. Shiren\r\nthe Wanderer is the 2nd entry in the series, departing from the Dragon Quest universe. Many people\r\noutside of Japan are familiar with various titles in the Pokemon Mystery Dungeon series, but Mystery\r\nDungeon also includes Chocobo Dungeon, Etrian Mystery Dungeon, as well as several other Dragon Quest\r\nrelated Mystery Dungeon series. It is quite popular in Japan!</p>\n<p>Mystery Dungeon are games similar to rogue (being a \"true roguelike\"), featuring Dungeon Crawling,\r\nTile base movement, Turn-based, and RPG-mechanics such as equipment, Defeating Monsters for EXP,\r\nItems, Equipment.</p>\n<p>Every time you step into the dungeon, if you die, you are sent back to the start with no inventory.\r\nShiren the Wanderer does not feature much \"meta-progression\". The only thing you can keep with you\r\nis the knowledge you gained from your attempts. However, some Dungeons in the Mystery Dungeon series\r\nallow you to bring items that you've previously obtained into the Dungeon.</p>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#what-is-mystery-dungeon\">What is Mystery Dungeon?</a></li>\n</ul>","headings":[{"id":"What-is-Mystery-Dungeon","value":"What is Mystery Dungeon?","depth":2}]},"allMarkdownRemark":{"edges":[{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/dungeons/feis-final-problem","title":"Feis Final Problem"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/dungeons/food-god","title":"Food God"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/dungeons/scroll-cave","title":"Scroll Cave"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/dungeons","title":"Dungeons"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/","title":"Top Page"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/guides","title":"Guides"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/items","title":"Items"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/other","title":"Other"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/system","title":"System"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/thanks","title":"Credits & Thanks"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/dungeons/table-mountain","title":"Table Mountain"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/guides/basics","title":"Basics"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/guides/blank-scroll-guide","title":"Blank Scroll Guide"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/guides/strategies","title":"Strategies"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/items/arrows","title":"Arrows"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/items/bracers","title":"Bracers"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/items/food","title":"Food"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/items/meat","title":"Meat"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/items/herbs","title":"Herbs"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/items/price-chart","title":"Price Chart"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/items/pots"